KELOVE 内容管理系统
===============

### 项目地址：

[【Coding:】https://xqitw.coding.net/public/django-kelove-cms/django-kelove-cms/git](https://xqitw.coding.net/public/django-kelove-cms/django-kelove-cms/git)

### 安装说明：

+ 该模块依赖 [django-kelove-admin](https://xqitw.coding.net/public/django-kelove-admin/django-kelove-admin/git),须先配置 `django-kelove-admin`

+ 该模块只提供后台管理，无前端界面，须额外安装前端模块包。例如：[django-kelove-cms-project](https://xqitw.coding.net/public/django-kelove-cms/django-kelove-cms-project/git)

### 需要加载的应用模块

```python

INSTALLED_APPS = [
    ...
    'django_kelove_cms',
    ...
]

```

### 需要添加的路由

```python

# 根url下添加以下路由
urlpatterns = [
    ...
     # kelove CMS
     path('cms/', include('django_kelove_cms.urls', namespace='django_kelove_cms')),
    ...
]

```

### 添加配置配置

```python

# 路由配置（可选）
KELOVE_CMS_URL_SETTINGS = {
    "tag_url": r'^tag/(?P<pk>[\w-]+)/page/(?P<page>[\w-]+)/$',
    "tag_home_url": r'^tag/(?P<pk>[\w-]+)/$',

    "category_url": r'^category/(?P<pk>[\w-]+)/page/(?P<page>[\w-]+)/$',
    "category_home_url": r'^category/(?P<pk>[\w-]+)/$',

    "document_url": r'^(?P<pk>[\w-]+)/page/(?P<page>[\w-]+)/$',
    "document_home_url": r'^(?P<pk>[\w-]+).html$',

    "search_url": r'^search/page/(?P<page>[\w-]+)/$',
    "search_home_url": r'^search/$',
}

```
